3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
4. the fan of gospel is the person who growsaconite##1
5. the mexican is the fan of salsa##1
6. the argentine is the person who growsdaisy##1
7. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
8. the person who growszinnia is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the fan of jazz##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
