4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, mouse, rabbit
1. the person who likes coral is not the fan of reggae##6
2. the fan of country is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the fan of blues##7
3. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes coral is somewhere between the fan of country and the person who likes yellow##7
5. the person who likes yellow is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the mouse is the person who likes fuchsia##1
8. the fan of blues is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| Color      | yellow  | coral | emerald | fuchsia |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | d&b  | country  | blues    |
| Pet           | rabbit | cat  | horse    | mouse    |

