.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, lemonade, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, magic-tricks, photography
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, mystery, romance, comedy
1. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
3. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
4. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
8. the person drinking lemonade is not the person watching zombie movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk     | lemonade | 7up        | fanta       |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | chess    | filmmaking | photography |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | mystery  | zombie    | romance   |

