.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, march, january
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, water-polo, weightlifting
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, scooter, snowmobile
1. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person driving the scooter##6
2. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
3. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
4. the person driving the boat is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
5. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person driving the snowmobile##7
8. the person driving the scooter is not the person who's birthday is in march##6
9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Birthday   | september      | august | january  | march    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | baseball  | water-polo | surfing    |
| Transport     | jet-ski       | boat      | scooter    | snowmobile |

