.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-11::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, r&b, rock
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indonesian, mexican, nigerian
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, whist, mah-jongg
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the indonesian##5
3. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
4. the fan of d&b is between the indonesian and the person playing mah-jongg##2
5. the nigerian is not the fan of r&b##6
6. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
7. the person playing mah-jongg is the mexican##1
8. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
9. the nigerian is somewhere between the person playing scrabble and the fan of blues##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | d&b        | r&b        | rock   |
| Nationality   | mexican | nigerian   | indonesian | french |
| Game           | mah-jongg  | whist | scrabble       | backgammon |

